name: NORMAL PEOPLE SCARE ME VINTAGE FLANNEL
description:
NORMAL PEOPLE SCARE ME VINTAGE FLANNEL Vintage Unisex Flannel Shirt(One of a Kind)

You know you're thinking it, so why not wear it plastered on your back for the world to see? Each flannel shirt is hand picked (assuring the best vintage quality) and screen printed with love. These flannel shirts are worn in and extremely comfortable.

Because these flannel shirts are vintage, they may have imperfections (small holes, worn areas, discolorations, fraying, etc.) including imperfections in the graphics due to variations in the clothing material printed on. That's what we call "vintage one of a kind"!

Machine wash cold. Tumble dry low. Do not bleach. Do not dry clean. Do not iron print.

Screen printed Vintage Piece 
The screen print " NORMAL PEOPLE SCARE ME" is in white and is all hand screenprinted by me!

All sales are final


ONE SIZE FITS ALL 
If you are worried about sizes please contact me and I can help you figure it out! 
:)

name: GALAXY SHORTS
description:
GALAXY SHORTS

One of a kind galaxy shorts! Each pair is unique in its own way. No two are ever exactly the same! I am the only one that produces galaxy comfy sweatshorts. All other galaxy shorts on the market are denim! These are much comfier and stylish!

The color wont fade, and doesn't have a rough feeling to it i use only premium paint. 
(I ship the pants unwashed because they need around 72 hours for the paint to set, so when you get the pants the paint will feel slightly coarse and will smell of paint so throw them in the washer before wearing them!)

Waist is stretchy/adjustable. So really every size fits width ways, it just depends on how long you want them. If you have questions on sizing please contact me and I'll be glad to answer them :)
(The strings on the shorts don't tie to tighten or loosen the shorts, the waist is just stretchy)

50% cotton , 50% polyester 


Takes about 1-2 weeks to ship to US.

PLEASE EMAIL ME IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS
